---
title: Grilled Sausage Flatbreads with Basil
description: All the fun of pizza night, on the grill! Flatbreads make an easy base for building personal 'pizzas'.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pains-plats-a-la-saucisse-grillee-941947a9.jpg
